://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\"}, {\"begin\": 302, \"end\": 317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 331, \"to\": 338}, {\"ngram\": \"the outgoing government\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 377}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 399}, {\"ngram\": \"at least mid\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 419}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 420, \"to\": 426}, {\"ngram\": \"no new prime minister\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 458}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 492}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 496, \"to\": 513}, {\"ngram\": \"a move\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 521}, {\"ngram\": \"the left-wing opposition\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 546}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"denial\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 569}, {\"ngram\": \"democracy\", \"from\": 573, \"to\": 582}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Macron intends to control the timetable, following the turmoil that ensued after he dissolved parliament and called a snap election on 9 June.\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 728, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 586, \"end\": 592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.246233343627571e-43, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the timetable\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 625}, {\"ngram\": \"the turmoil\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 648}, {\"ngram\": \"parliament\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 690}, {\"ngram\": \"a snap election\", \"from\": 702, \"to\