"the post\", \"from\": 1903, \"to\": 1911}, {\"ngram\": \"prime minister\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 1929}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 37-year-old Castets is a senior civil servant specialising in \\\"the repression of tax fraud and financial crime\\\", according to an NFP press release.\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 2083, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1948, \"end\": 1955, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Castets_(grape)\", \"score\": 0.5009607382045541, \"rank\": 0.6944444444443503, \"text\": \"Castets\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Castets_(grape)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Castets_(grape)\"}, {\"begin\": 2065, \"end\": 2068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Federation_Party\", \"score\": 0.9999999999336069, \"rank\": 6.546331440651546e-11, \"text\": \"NFP\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Federation_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Federation_Party\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a senior civil servant\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 1981}, {\"ngram\": \"the repression\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2013}, {\"ngram\": \"tax fraud\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2026}, {\"ngram\": \"financial crime\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2046}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She is also the director of finance and procurement in the administration of the City of Paris, headed by the Socialist mayor Anne Hidalgo.\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2223, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2210, \"end\": 2222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anne Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the director\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2108}, {\"ngram\": \"finance\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2119}, {\"ngram\": \"procurement\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2135}, {\"ngram\": \"the administration\", \"from\": 2139, \"to\": 2157}, {\"ngram\": \"the City\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2169}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2178}, {\"ngram\": \"the Socialist mayor\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2209}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Interviewedon France Inter on 24 July, Castets said she wanted to \\\"look for coalitions\\\" but without allying herself with the presidential camp, which is accused of cutting public services and lowering taxes for the wealthiest.\", \"from\": 2225, \"to\": 2451, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2239, \"end\": 2251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_Inter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"France Inter\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_Inter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_Inter\"}, {\"begin\": 2264, \"end\": 2271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Castets_(grape)\", \"score\": 0.5009607382045541, \"rank\": 0.6944444444443503, \"text\": \"Castets\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Castets_(grape)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Castets_(grape)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"24 July\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2262}, {\"ngram\": \"coalitions\", \"from\": 2301, \"to\": 2311}, {\"ngram\": \"the presidential camp\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2367}, {\"ngram\": \"public services\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2412}, {\"ngram\": \"taxes\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2431}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We will be building agreements [in the National Assembly] on subject after subject\\\", she added.\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2549, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2493, \"end\": 2510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Assembly\", \"score\": 0.9999999077022081, \"rank\": 8.716386047269537e-08, \"text\": \"National Assembly\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Assembly\", \"dbpedia\": \"